# Shared — Pub/Sub Push Receiver
# M17-S02: Pub/Sub POSTs each message here when PUBSUB_CONSUMER_MODE=push.
# Authenticated by PubSubPushGuard (Google OIDC bearer token), NOT X-Internal-Key —
# this route is @Public() so InternalApiGuard is bypassed for it.
#
# To exercise locally:
#   1. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run dev
#   2. APP_ENV=local (the default) bypasses PubSubPushGuard entirely — no real Authorization
#      header is needed below. The guard only enforces when APP_ENV != local.
#
# The `data` field below is base64(JSON.stringify(domainEvent)) — this sample encodes
# {"eventId":"...","eventName":"StubEvent","tenantId":"...", ...} for a handler registered
# under subscription "ikaro-StubEvent-test-consumer". Swap for a real registered subscription
# name + a real event envelope to test a specific consumer.

@baseUrl = {{backendUrl}}

### POST /pubsub/push — happy path (guard disabled locally)
POST {{baseUrl}}/pubsub/push
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": {
    "data": "eyJldmVudElkIjoiMDFqZDBmYWtlLWlkIiwidGVuYW50SWQiOiJ0ZW5hbnQtMSIsIm9jY3VycmVkQXQiOiIyMDI2LTA3LTA5VDAwOjAwOjAwLjAwMFoiLCJjb3JyZWxhdGlvbklkIjoiY29ycmVsYXRpb24tMSIsImV2ZW50TmFtZSI6IlN0dWJFdmVudCIsImV2ZW50VmVyc2lvbiI6MSwiZGF0YSI6eyJ2YWx1ZSI6ImhlbGxvIn19",
    "messageId": "test-message-1",
    "attributes": { "eventName": "StubEvent" },
    "deliveryAttempt": 1
  },
  "subscription": "projects/ikaro-local/subscriptions/ikaro-StubEvent-test-consumer"
}

###

### POST /pubsub/push — missing Authorization header → 403 (requires APP_ENV=staging or production
### temporarily — under the local default the guard is bypassed and this would 204 instead)
POST {{baseUrl}}/pubsub/push
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": {
    "data": "eyJ0ZXN0IjoidHJ1ZSJ9",
    "messageId": "test-message-2",
    "attributes": {}
  },
  "subscription": "projects/ikaro-local/subscriptions/ikaro-StubEvent-test-consumer"
}

###

### POST /pubsub/push — invalid/expired bearer token → 403 (same APP_ENV caveat as above)
POST {{baseUrl}}/pubsub/push
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer invalid-or-expired-token

{
  "message": {
    "data": "eyJ0ZXN0IjoidHJ1ZSJ9",
    "messageId": "test-message-3",
    "attributes": {}
  },
  "subscription": "projects/ikaro-local/subscriptions/ikaro-StubEvent-test-consumer"
}

###

### POST /pubsub/push — unregistered subscription name → acked (204), no handler invoked
POST {{baseUrl}}/pubsub/push
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": {
    "data": "eyJ0ZXN0IjoidHJ1ZSJ9",
    "messageId": "test-message-4",
    "attributes": {}
  },
  "subscription": "projects/ikaro-local/subscriptions/ikaro-NoSuchConsumer"
}

###
